Simple plain text exporter for demo purposes

See http://www.grantlee.org/apidox/for_themers.html for more information


Texture data:
    texture.width  = 982
    texture.height = 1133

    texture.trimmedName = textures
    texture.fullName = textures.png
    texture.absoluteFileName = G:/Projects/GITHub/MedusaVST/Assets/textures.png

SmartUpdateHash: $TexturePacker:SmartUpdate:c8c6fbc72876643cd300456ac993fc41$

Sprite data:

There are 2 variants:
- sprites - contains the sprites, aliases are available in the
  aliasList property and are not added top level

- allSprites - list of all sprites

Load javascript filter plugin, must be located in the exporter's folder in a subfolder
grantlee/0.2/makecssselector.qs



    =========================================================================

    Use the javascript filter plugin to replace -hover with :hover
    but_1_off.png

    -- name without image type extension
    sprite.trimmedName      = but_1_off

    -- name with image extension
    sprite.fullName         = but_1_off.png

    -- offset of the center of the trimmed sprite from the
    -- center of the original sprite (used by cocos2d)
    sprite.absoluteOffset.x = 
    sprite.absoluteOffset.y = 

    -- list of alias sprites for this one
    sprite.aliasList = 

    --- frame rectangle with pixel coordinates
    sprite.frameRect.x = 202
    sprite.frameRect.y = 1106
    sprite.frameRect.width = 22
    sprite.frameRect.height = 25

    --- frame rectangle with uv coordinates (0..1)
    sprite.frameRectRel.x = 0.205702647657841
    sprite.frameRectRel.y = 0.976169461606355
    sprite.frameRectRel.width = 0.0224032586558045
    sprite.frameRectRel.height = 0.0220653133274493

    --- version of the frame rect with "original" width and height
    sprite.frameRectWithoutRotation.x = 202
    sprite.frameRectWithoutRotation.y = 1106
    sprite.frameRectWithoutRotation.width = 22
    sprite.frameRectWithoutRotation.height = 25

    -- true if the sprite was rotated
    sprite.rotated        = false

    -- true if the sprite was trimmed
    sprite.trimmed        = true

    sprite.sourceRect.x = 4
    sprite.sourceRect.y = 2
    sprite.sourceRect.width = 22
    sprite.sourceRect.height = 25

    sprite.cornerOffset.x = 4
    sprite.cornerOffset.y = 2

    sprite.untrimmedSize.width = 26
    sprite.untrimmedSize.height = 27

    -- the file absolute file name of the sprite
    sprite.fileData.absoluteFileName = G:/Projects/GITHub/MedusaVST/Source/VST/resources/buttons/but_1_off.png

    -- the modification date of the sprite
    sprite.fileData.lastModified = 2012-05-27T20:00:36

    -- the creation date of the sprite
    sprite.fileData.created = 2012-11-17T17:07:48

    -- the file size of the sprite
    sprite.fileData.fileSize = 1694
